
'''Beauty''' ni filime yo muri [[Afurika]] yepfo ya 2011 yanditswe kandi iyobowe na Oliver Hermanus<ref>https://mubi.com/films/beauty-2011</ref> . Yerekanwe bwa mbere mu gice cya Un Certain Regard mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Cannes 2011<ref>https://www.filmaffinity.com/us/film195631.html</ref> .   Iyi filime yatoranijwe nk'iyinjira muri Afurika y'Epfo muri Filime nziza y'ururimi rw'amahanga mu bihembo bya 84 bya Osama,   ariko ntabwo yakoze urutonde rwa nyuma<ref>https://www.videodetective.com/movie/beauty-26595</ref> 

