== Kwakira neza ==
Filime yakiriwe neza n'abayireba. Isubiramo ryegeranya Rotten Tomatoes ivuga ko 83% by'abanegura umwuga bahaye filime isuzuma ryiza, naho impuzandengo ya 6.8 kuri 10. <ref>http://www.filmblerg.com/2012/07/31/film-review-beauty-2011/</ref> Abenshi mu banegura bashimye imikorere ya Deon Lotz <nowiki>, Peter Bradshaw wo muri ''</nowiki> ''The Guardian'' 'yise "Igikorwa gikomeye, ariko cyihishe kandi kitoroshye"<ref>https://roobla.com/16913/beauty-skoonheid-2011-movie-review/</ref> .  David Parkinson wo mu kinyamakuru Empire Magazine na we yashimye Lotz, kandi mu nyenyeri eshatu kuri eshanu zasuzumye incamake y'urubanza rwe agira ati: "Nubwo iri zina, hari imbaraga mbi kuri ubu bushakashatsi bwo gutwarwa n'uburakari<ref>https://www.simbasible.com/beauty-movie-review/</ref>." 

== Ibihembo ==
''Ubwiza'' bwahawe igihembo cya Queer Palm mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Cannes 2011.  Umukinnyi Deon Lotz yakiriwe bidasanzwe mu iserukiramuco rya Filime rya Zurich 2011 kubera ibikorwa bye muri iyi filime<ref>https://alchetron.com/Beauty-(2011-film)</ref>.

